description:
PANTS with Kate Moennig and Leisha Hailey

Produced by Melisa D. Monts and Diamond MPrint Productions

Edited by Diane Kang 

 

Kate convinces Leisha to get into surf skating. Leisha finds out her sister is 2% French. And together they become amateur soccer logo art critics, international travel guides, and proficient detectors of bullsh*t. Or they try at least.
